This paper deals with natural language understanding and generation, specifically the processing of Multiword Expressions (MWEs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves statistical models and semantic clustering, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the diversity in lexical, syntactical, and semantic properties of MWEs, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.NE).
